Descriptions of transportation price indexes

TP.FG.J07 07.ULATIRMA TP.FG.J071 071.ARA SATIN ALIMI TP.FG.J072 072.KSEL ULATIRMA ARALARININ LETM TP.FG.J073 073.ULATIRMA HZMETLER

4 different price indexes that are related to the transportation industry seems to be linearly corralate between each other. Thus only using one of them will be enough. TP.FG.J071 will be used for this purposes since it is the most contextually related one to the production of automobiles.
